width=\"195\">17</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 119px;\" width=\"215\">3.3</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 87px;\" width=\"210\">-871.7</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 54px;\" width=\"70\">Yes</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3><a name=\"configurations\" id=\"configurations\"></a>Configurations</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><a name=\"how-to-set-up-a-order-pack-optimization\" id=\"how-to-set-up-a-order-pack-optimization\"></a><a id=\"orderpack\" name=\"orderpack\"></a>How to set up a Order pack Optimization?</h4>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"computer_code\">\r\n<p>/itemlocation/api/itemlocation/itemLocation/save</p>\r\n\r\n<p>{&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;ProtectionLevel&quot;: &quot;MAX&quot;,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;UomId&quot;: &quot;EACH&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;LeadTime&quot;: 7.0,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;PurchasePrice&quot;: 10.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;CarryingCost&quot;:0.25,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;InboundFixedCost&quot;: 41.0,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;InboundVariableCost&quot;: 42.0,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;OutboundFixedCost&quot;: 43.0,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;OutboundVariableCost&quot;: 44.0</p>\r\n&nbsp; },&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Evaluate Max Extra Carrying Cost and Max Extra Carrying Cost Percent:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>The maximum extra&nbsp;carrying cost is acceptable if the order quantity is rounded up to a pack size greater than the base packaging UOM.&nbsp;The extra&nbsp;carrying cost is the additional carrying cost compared to the base (EACH) UOM. If the extra&nbsp;carrying cost is greater than this limit, the pack size will not be considered as an eligible pack.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"computer_code\">\r\n<p>/itemlocation/api/itemlocation/itemLocation/save</p>\r\n\r\n<p>{&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;MaxExtraCarryingCost&quot;:2,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;MaxExtraCarryingCostPercent&quot;:null,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;UseOrderPackOptimization&quot;:true</p>\r\n&nbsp; },&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The maximum extra carrying cost % that is acceptable for the pack size to be eligible for selection. The extra carrying cost % is a % increase in carrying cost compared to using the base (EACH) UOM. If the extra carrying cost % is greater than this limit, the pack size will not be considered as an eligible pack.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"computer_code\">\r\n<p>/itemlocation/api/itemlocation/itemLocation/save</p>\r\n\r\n<p>{&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;MaxExtraCarryingCost&quot;:null,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;MaxExtraCarryingCostPercent&quot;:5,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;UseOrderPackOptimization&quot;:true</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; },&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><a name=\"services\" id=\"services\"></a>Services</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;APIs listed in the following table are referenced in this document. Refer to the API documentation for additional details on&nbsp;each service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" height=\"195\" width=\"740\">\r\n\t<thead>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\"><strong><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Service</font></strong></th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\"><strong>Component</strong></th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\"><strong>Group</strong></th>\r\n\t\t\t<th scope=\"col\"><strong><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Service Endpoint</font></strong></th>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</thead>\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>OrederPackOptimizat